title: Plat 2 Supp (last season) LF duo
body:
Hello friends!

As stated in the title, I'm a supp main and was plat 2 last season. Looking for eligible duo partners!

Would pref ADC mains as I'm well over the struggle of playing with random ADCs every game but I'm open to whatever at this point!
My IGN is Phoénix, feel free to add me and message me in client, no reply here is necessary.

It's been a rough start to the season, let's turn things around!
